title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 6 2022
description:
They trampled on our rights! Buck says the point to hammer home is they "trampled on them and they were wrong." J&J shot found to be unsafe. Clay says, "I don't know how you trust the government anymore." Soviet Mary Poppins: "Kamala Harris slept her way to the top" is disinformation regardless of her long-ago behavior with powerbrokers like former San Francisco Mayor Willie Brown that has been reported. Why the SCOTUS leak is so dangerous: Protesters go to justices' homes. Clay reasserts Chief Justice Roberts, to protect safety, should do what he must and put out decision ASAP. Psaki to be replaced by first black, gay press secretary. Psaki won't answer if Biden approves of abortion at 9 months.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
